<td class="d-block comment-body markdown-body  js-comment-body">

          <p>Chain of events:</p>
<ol>
<li>Open app</li>
<li>Log in (if not already logged in)</li>
<li>Swipe to "Content Feeds"</li>
<li>Add by clicking the plus sign (+)</li>
<li>Long press the added item and delete it by clicking the minus sign (-)</li>
<li>Try clicking the minus sign again ( -)</li>
<li>Repeat 5 and 6 until it crashes.</li>
</ol>
<p>Or<br>
4. Hit the minus sign<br>
5. Hit Home (get out of the app)<br>
6. Open the app again<br>
7. Hit the minus sign again - App crash<br>
8. Repeat if necessary. Crash "works" on the Sony "low end" test phone</p>
<p>The crash log:</p>
